mobs.keywords: squirrel playful ball grey playful-ball grey-squirrel fur
mobs.long_desc: A playful ball of grey fur is climbing at your feet.
mobs.desc: You see a very playful squirrel, it tugs at your pockets almost like a little thief. Better watch out.

mobs.long_desc: A small black rodent brandishes his white stripes.
mobs.desc: This creature smells rather odd and looks like trouble. Stay away!

mobs.long_desc: A rabbit scurries through the brush.
mobs.desc: You notice a really cute bunny hopping by you. Its soft fur brushes you lightly as it runs by. What is it running from?

mobs.long_desc: A ball of needles is eyeing you cautiously.
mobs.desc: About as large as a baby pig, this creature has four short, stubby legs leading down to delicate black-clawed paws.  Its snout is slender and almost doglike, and it snarls as it walks, revealing little pointed white teeth.  By far, though, its most conspicuous feature is its coat of long barbed needles, bristling and making faint rustling noises with every move the animal makes.

mobs.long_desc: A large deer with a white tail jumps from your path.
mobs.desc: He is a four-legged creature with long legs ending in dainty hooves. An impressive rack of antlers tops his head, and his tail flashes white when he leaps.

mobs.long_desc: A ferocious wolverine glares at you from its hole.
mobs.desc: You see a small but mean ball of fur with some really sharp teeth. It seems to be glaring back at you and looks ready to BITE!

mobs.long_desc: A bobcat is slowly stalking its prey.
mobs.desc: You look upon a fast and stealthy cat of prey in the woods. This must be what the other animals are running from. It's sleek and mean looking, and looks as though it's stalking you.

mobs.long_desc: A large black bear regards you warily from a bush.
mobs.desc: This large bear has a thick, dense coat of dark brown fur.  He squints at things around him in a most dubious manner, occasionally padding this way or that on huge paws.  He snuffles and sneezes sometimes.

mobs.long_desc: A dark brown wolf runs through the woods after a rabbit.
mobs.desc: This large doglike creature has a shaggy coat of brown fur and glistening white fangs. He moves with an agile and cunning grace.

mobs.long_desc: A ferret darts about then stands on its rear legs, scanning for danger.
mobs.desc: Except for the smell, this thin creatures is so cute you could just cuddle it forever. It seems to think differently about you as it shows you its needle-like teeth.

mobs.keywords: grizzly-bear bear grizzly brown-bear brown mammoth
mobs.long_desc: A mammoth brown bear is snarling at you!
mobs.desc: This huge bear looks mean and very hungry. His coat is long and shaggy, dense and warm, and his paws are absolutely huge, ending in black claws. When he snarls, which is often, his impressive white teeth can be easily seen.

mobs.long_desc: A small furry rodent peeks from its hole in the ground.
mobs.desc: You notice a simple furry rodent eyeing you from across the fields. It looks harmless enough.

mobs.long_desc: A wild grey coyote sniffs the air for prey.
mobs.desc: This wolf-like creature is a bit scruffier and rangier than a wolf, with spindly legs and a tail that's not as bushy as a wolf's. His snout is longer and his nose bigger, and he doesn't seem nearly as hostile.

mobs.long_desc: A huge buffalo stands in the serene wilderness.
mobs.desc: This animal is HUGE and looks calm in all this wilderness. Its size is unreal and you think it could feed you and your party for days.

mobs.long_desc: A brash wild horse challenges you to pass.
mobs.desc: You look upon one of the wildest animals you have ever seen.  This horse looks to have had little contact with man or dwarf because it seems not to fear you. It actually runs at you in an attempt to chase you off.

mobs.long_desc: A small yellow and brown duck splashes you.
mobs.desc: You see an extremely cute little duck floating by you. It doesn't look like it appreciates your looks though.

mobs.long_desc: A large goose waddles by you, honking. It begs to be kicked.
mobs.desc: Aarrgghhhh! How annoying! This large white bird is actually snapping at you, making this awful HONK sound.

mobs.keywords: alligator gator teeth strange pair eyes nikozian-alligator
mobs.long_desc: A strange pair of eyes looks at you from under the surface of the water.
mobs.desc: All you seem to notice are TEETH attached to a large mouth!

mobs.long_desc: A man floats by searching for a catch.
mobs.desc: This man looks very tan as though he's been here all his life. He looks somewhat nomadic, and is expertly catching fish.

mobs.long_desc: A caribou is here, grazing on the tundra.
mobs.desc: You see a large herd animal with really large antlers.  It's challenging you with those antlers right now!

mobs.keywords: ancient duergar dwarf warrior guard general ancient-dwarf
mobs.long_desc: An ancient dwarf rests here reminiscing about the good ole days.
mobs.desc: This evil little dwarf is old!  He's mumbling stories of ancient battles long past with humans and elves.  He looks to have been a very important duergar at one time, a general perhaps?

mobs.long_desc: A mountain dwarf stands here guarding his realm.
mobs.desc: The long matted beard and facial scars of what is exposed on his face scowl at you. This dwarf looks like he means business. He's well trained and looks to be guarding these hills from evil intruders.

mobs.long_desc: A common dwarf is strolling through the hills.
mobs.desc: This dwarf looks unaware of the surrondings as he walks about looking for food and shelter.  His beard is matted with the clay of the hills but he seems undaunted by the harshness of the land.

mobs.long_desc: A falcon streaks from the sky upon some prey.
mobs.desc: You see large bird of dark brown and tan feathers. It swoops from the sky at smaller prey. You wonder if that last pass it made was to see if you were small enough?

mobs.long_desc: A chamois stands here, defiantly challenging you.
mobs.desc: He's a large goat covered in long, fuzzy, light-brown hair. His long, spiralling horns are evidence of his maturity, and his eyes look almost insanely aggressive.

mobs.long_desc: A proud pack animal hides from the cold under its wool.
mobs.desc: You see a tall and very furry pack animal that looks somewhat friendly. It scans the area for some bushes to munch upon.

mobs.long_desc: You sense a presence sneaking through the hills.
mobs.desc: You barely notice a shifting in the background, and then realize it is a dwarven thief! He seems to be eyeing your pockets, so watch him closely.

mobs.long_desc: An old dwarven woman is rambling through the hills.
mobs.desc: This dwarven woman is old! She looks peaceful though. She's just easily walking through the hills chasing the dwarven children.

mobs.long_desc: A small dwarf looks lost in the hills.
mobs.desc: You see a little brat causing trouble. He plays mischievously about the land teasing and taunting all in his path.

mobs.long_desc: A small merchant approaches you for a deal.
mobs.desc: This merchant doesn't look very trustworthy. He approaches you for a deal and looks very well dressed for a dwarf.

mobs.long_desc: A large elk is here, grazing on the tundra.
mobs.desc: You see a huge grazing animal. Its antlers are wide and monstrous. It looks as though it can and has fought a grizzly bear. It looks at you with interest.

mobs.long_desc: A small white rabbit is hiding in a snow drift.
mobs.desc: You almost don't notice this pure white creature against some of the snow drifts. It darts about fearfully, but you think you may be able to catch it.

mobs.long_desc: A dwarven priest rests here praying to his god.
mobs.desc: This dwarf looks distracted as if in meditation to his god. He is dressed in non-descript leathers and carries a simple holy symbol.

mobs.long_desc: A frail looking womam passes by.
mobs.desc: This woman looks elven and wears the clothes of a mighty magic user.  Her fiery pendants and and robe almost seem ablaze!

mobs.keywords: deer white-tailed-deer large-deer white-tail whitetail fearlesswhitehart
mobs.long_desc: A large deer with a white tail jumps from your path.
mobs.desc: He is a four-legged creature with long legs ending in dainty hooves.  An impressive rack of antlers tops his head, and his tail flashes white when he leaps.

mobs.long_desc: A fearless white buck looks serenely in your direction.
mobs.desc: The noblest of the forest animals, the white hart is sacred to Azkrael, Goddess of the Hunt.  It is said that one who slays the white hart without the permission of the Gods themselves is cursed for ten years.  Just seeing this majestic creature is a once-in-a-lifetime occurence for most people.

objects.ground: A set of reptile scales looks abandoned here.

extras.text: These boots look to be excellently crafted from several alligator hides.  They are water resistant, sturdy, and light.

objects.ground: A brown metal band has been discarded here.

extras.text: It is a simple and primitive narrow sheet of bronze bent into a bracelet.  It offers some simple protection.

objects.ground: A crudely forged band of red metal lies here.

extras.text: This crudely forged band of heavy iron looks to be very protective.  It is inscribed with many mysterious runes.

objects.short: a spiked iron buckler rimmed in mythril
objects.ground: What looks like a large bowl with sharp spines is almost hidden here.

extras.text: This ancient piece of armor looks incredibly ornate and protective.  It is heavy and look intimidating.  It's polished mythril rim would blind an enemy in the sun.  A prize to be guarded.

objects.ground: Some bulky-looking armored boots lie here forgotten.

extras.text: These boots look incredibly well-armored, heavy and bulky too.  They are crudely forged of iron and rimmed with what looks like polished silver.

objects.ground: What looks like a simple spike lies here forgotten.

extras.text: This is a simple iron spike.  It looks incredibly sharp and could probably do some damage.

objects.ground: A small bloodstained double-bladed axe lies discarded here.

extras.text: This heavy iron Beast looks mean, and like it could cause an enemy some problems.  Its covered with blood and runes.

objects.short: a leather shield rimmed in mythril
objects.ground: A well-oiled leather buckler rimmed in a brilliant silver rests here.

extras.text: This covering seem to act well as a shield.  It's well made and is supported by a silvery metal.  The leather is thick and hard against a battle.

objects.ground: A pile of thick leather sits in a corner.

extras.text: A simple raw leather sheet sewen at the edges so as not to fray.  It looks like it provides simple armor against battle, and the elements.

objects.ground: A large leather cloak with strange markings lies here.

extras.text: This piece of thick leather has been expertly tanned and burnt with many odd runes.  It looks to be a good piece of protection.

objects.ground: A spiked mace with runes has been left here.

extras.text: You look upon one mean looking mace.  It has four spikes about it's globe and is covered in strange runes.

objects.ground: A small bowl-shaped watercraft is sitting here.

extras.text: This small watercraft is oval-shaped, with a single small bench in the middle. It is constructed of a round frame of branches over which the skins of buffalo have been stretched.  It looks like it's limited to a single human-sized occupant.  The bottom is stained much darker than the rest, apparently due to the body of water in which it has spent much time: Black Lake.

objects.ground: A shiny slimy fish lies here, recently gutted.

extras.text: Though uncooked, this fish looks mighty tasty.  It is the gutted body of a lake perch.  It has small scales and a short fat body.  Its nearly white flesh has a mild taste that should make for an enjoyable meal.

objects.ground: A long, sharp quill lies on the ground here.

extras.text: It's an extra-long quill from the back of an Eldorian Porcupine.  Though extremely painful when jabbed into bare flesh, young punk sorcerers use these as quills for scribing spells.  Being thinner than a bird feather, they make impressive, spidery-looking letters but also break more easily.

rooms.name: The Nikozian Trail
rooms.description: You stand along a well traveled path that looks worn in the surrounding earth for many hundreds of years.  It's rocky in most places as though it were purposefully lined in stone to preserve the pathway for many years.  From here the view of the surrounding lands is breathtaking.  The trail runs north- south here.

North.description: The Nikozian Trail runs to the north.

South.description: To the south, you see the Northern Swamp Road.

rooms.name: The Black Woods Trail
rooms.description: The trail is made up of tracks of wagons and verious beasts.  And has pushed back the thick bushes to show the forest is wild and alive.  Many animals run the land and tall trees keep much of the forest floor blanked in a dark shadow. Passage of the road is difficult but you can seem to squeeze through the brush in places.  The trail continues to the north and south.

North.description: The woods continue to the north.

East.description: The woods continue to the east.

rooms.name: The Nikozian Trail
rooms.description: You stand along a well traveled path that looks worn in the surrounding earth for many hundreds of years.  It's rocky in most places as though it were purposefully lined in stone to preserve the pathway for many years.  From here the view of the surrounding lands is breathtaking.  The trail runs south- west here.

North.description: You see a dark, ominous wood.

East.description: You see a dark, ominous wood.

South.description: The trail continues to the south.
